Rita Daniels, actress and mother of Nollywood diva Regina Daniels is now more than ever growing younger.

The beautiful mother has shared the most recent photos of her stunning in a white lace dress.

She shared her adorable outfit to celebrate valentine’s day adding a message of the gospel to it.

“Arise and Shine for We are the Light of the world. Send the light for everyone around to see and how great to know that Jesus lives and reigns forever. May we shine forth IJN, amen!!”, she wrote.



			
